    {
      "review_id": "Hklezu2Z6Q",
      "rebuttal_id": "H1gYO-8SC7",
      "sentence_index": 17,
      "text": "Furthermore, in DQN, the Q-value for the greedy action is used in the update, while in our setting, we do not use greedy actions.",
